                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Why Recycle Electronics?</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              Electronics contain both valuable and hazardous materials. When disposed of properly, up to 95% of materials can be recovered. This conserves natural resources and reduces mining needs. It prevents soil and water contamination. It keeps toxic substances out of landfills. This protects groundwater from harmful chemicals.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Visual break with recycling image -->
        <div class="relative mb-12 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
          <img src="/images/recycle-phone.jpeg" alt="Electronics being recycled" class="w-full h-64 object-cover">
