              <ul class="text-gray-700 space-y-1">
                <li>• Consumer drop-off locations</li>
                <li>• Corporate collection programs</li>
                <li>• Municipal collection events</li>
                <li>• Retailer take-back programs</li>
                <li>• Mail-in recycling services</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-blue-600 mb-3">Processing and Recovery</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">Sorted electronics undergo various processing steps:</p>
              <ul class="text-gray-700 space-y-1">
                <li>• Manual disassembly of components</li>
                <li>• Mechanical shredding and separation</li>
                <li>• Magnetic separation of ferrous metals</li>
                <li>• Optical sorting of plastics</li>
                <li>• Chemical extraction of precious metals</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-3">Recovered Materials</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">Electronics recycling recovers numerous valuable materials:</p>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
              <div>
                <h5 class="font-medium text-gray-800 mb-2">Metals</h5>
                <ul class="text-gray-600 text-sm space-y-1">
                  <li>• Copper</li>
                  <li>• Aluminum</li>
                  <li>• Steel</li>
                  <li>• Gold</li>
                  <li>• Silver</li>
                  <li>• Platinum</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h5 class="font-medium text-gray-800 mb-2">Rare Earth Elements</h5>
                <ul class="text-gray-600 text-sm space-y-1">
                  <li>• Neodymium</li>
                  <li>• Dysprosium</li>
                  <li>• Terbium</li>
                  <li>• Yttrium</li>
                  <li>• Europium</li>
                  <li>• Indium</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h5 class="font-medium text-gray-800 mb-2">Other Materials</h5>
